# Directory where Starkeep stores local data (config, db, objects, etc.)
# Defaults to ~/.starkeep if not set.
# STARKEEP_DATA_DIR=~/.starkeep
#
# TODO: Before this setting is fully usable, each consumer needs to be wired up:
#   - admin-web (Next.js): place .env.local at apps/admin-web/ — Next.js picks it up automatically.
#   - teardown-bootstrap.sh and other shell scripts: add `source` logic to load this file.
#   - tsx CLI scripts (cli-install-*.ts): add dotenv (or equivalent) to load this file at startup.
